You've been added as a housemate on roomiepayup.com
===============================================

You have been added as a housemate on roomiepayup.com by the financial administrator of your household.
Roomiepayup is an app to help administrate household finances.

When household bills are due, the household administrator will split the amount into shares and assign each share to a housemate with a due date for the share.
When a share has been assigned to you, you will receive a notification via email with the amount and due date of the share.

If you have any questions, please contact the financial administrator of your household.
